# cross_entropy.pl v0.1.0
# Author: MH Seabolt
# Last updated: 8-21-2021

# SYNOPSIS
# Calculates the cross entropy H(p,q) between two random variables X and Y, given as two input matrices P and Q.
# Expects that both matrices are formatted in the same way.

